{"id":"8b96008a7acd60ea1219e5666364f487cb9bb745a3156d413194dde6645c3bdf","item_id":"411c9a03b8:0","text":"Texture Manager（纹理管理器）的职责很简单：将图像转换为 RenderMan 的纹理格式，可使用 OpenImageIO 或"}
{"id":"f03ea00b18d9aa9880720aacfb2abc16fe6ae8e4342fd78d93c1c73a4059b349","item_id":"411c9a03b8:1","text":"txmake"}
{"id":"f03ea00b18d9aa9880720aacfb2abc16fe6ae8e4342fd78d93c1c73a4059b349","item_id":"411c9a03b8:17","text":"txmake"}
{"id":"b12d81bda6ee2d50bba01bdd0f1f304b1ec12cc5b5711c886371b3c098cf07d3","item_id":"411c9a03b8:2","text":"。它既处理单张图像，也处理纹理图集（UDIM、Mudbox、ZBrush）。"}
{"id":"2dafaf8717c37809cca191dc9ff347a96358a01e4112bf3aaf81b74191816f18","item_id":"411c9a03b8:3","text":"你可以在 Houdini 中选择 New Tab，然后在列表底部选择 RenderMan Texture Manager；该列表属于"}
{"id":"fed9cb4fb6337176c5433e992762e01b29899b0a8b42350c673be014797d46c6","item_id":"411c9a03b8:4","text":"New Pane Type（新窗格类型）"}
{"id":"493fbaf2489cdc9b4e5ff8ec7f4c8631d6f39665b020b3df01d72a447cbfe0c8","item_id":"411c9a03b8:6","text":"User interface（用户界面）"}
{"id":"9d260d70a564a6b9732f8d4f9a3fe1d0a19988a9a3c9eb7f829118306b2805e9","item_id":"411c9a03b8:7","text":"打开新场景时，Texture Manager 会找到所有作为纹理使用的图像，并将它们加入转换队列。转换设置会基于一组规则，这些规则定义在"}
{"id":"1fa06b0813ea7ac6c2328ce680d5bece8b6f442eff2bb21c6fd00f0c892b9b49","item_id":"411c9a03b8:8","text":"json file（JSON 文件）"}
{"id":"567e491093cdc903ce7d27bd4edb3942bb45d50c0a79c670e20da89ec8f4b8e7","item_id":"411c9a03b8:9","text":"中（见下文）。使用 Settings（设置）窗格修改当前所选图像的设置，然后点击 Apply（应用）按钮，用新设置重新转换图像。"}
{"id":"9ebc09f143940f86273ac841c63388e66f0514a57ae889f395eb77a6e6429ddd","item_id":"411c9a03b8:10","text":"只需按下"}
{"id":"2619addc5f5263a58287908d6ffe62a867ce90a736f960bc38b72de4a89fb10f","item_id":"411c9a03b8:11","text":"Parse Scene（解析场景）"}
{"id":"4163c9ef0682a38acf4b5984fddc4a3ef263b2be52f61d7ca515472106177ad7","item_id":"411c9a03b8:12","text":"即可在需要时转换新纹理。"}
{"id":"3db366bb36e035be494af7e55c591f0f089bdf4a95b35bb90fdfd6e63d56c775","item_id":"411c9a03b8:13","text":"Pick Images（选择图像）"}
{"id":"4c6c4fafb4070bbc9d509fa3450e230081576a911175970c3baf71e64c26965a","item_id":"411c9a03b8:15","text":"Pick Directories（选择目录）"}
{"id":"120edc8fb944a887c0060a678c996a786a7d63f4c49b5078b46ac494f9dcae3e","item_id":"411c9a03b8:16","text":"允许你预先转换图像，而不必了解如何使用 OpenImageIO 或"}
{"id":"08b6c7722f669f4561dba3e8a017912ce601202ccb4ae6fcc098d0a4ff5f6b8c","item_id":"411c9a03b8:19","text":"Stop / Start the conversion queue（停止/启动转换队列）"}
{"id":"3ec8a00accd44451eca9410fb0d8f942806e15a363d3fb56280c2a8d8e29e2b1","item_id":"411c9a03b8:20","text":"默认情况下，转换队列始终运行，但有时你可能希望停止转换过程。"}
{"id":"76afe180ddecac3fec86af3ae2ee1958b3a37a11e806d634efe77ee548794d35","item_id":"411c9a03b8:21","text":"可以点击进度条右侧的图标来停止和重新启动转换队列。队列停止时，正在运行的 txmake 进程会立即被终止，但已有纹理会保持不变。重新启动后，它会从上次停止的位置继续。"}
{"id":"9c2de3ba9d341ebfd32dbcafc884b2998f37f7407710339d9dfe3cedd1e4c3c9","item_id":"411c9a03b8:22","text":"Conversion information（转换信息）"}
{"id":"24d65a629a47cd09c586b271d03888e82c0cb05b7b3907fa8b57f5ced9108d5b","item_id":"411c9a03b8:23","text":"Texture Manager 窗口底部有磁盘用量和进度指示器。"}
{"id":"1e02c0819e6781cf8bdf90279f3088b7448d7a2811f985c453b21dac3da93eb3","item_id":"411c9a03b8:24","text":"列表中的每个文件也都有一个状态图标。"}
{"id":"729102f51d85e95cb27749a76ecc19eaab6efa9209f0b940ff36dcc91e5f1aac","item_id":"411c9a03b8:25","text":"交互式与 Batch 渲染"}
{"id":"43b7e4141020dc79aa112a7582f9e57bde3404d988b50b7703d7ac3db27223d4","item_id":"411c9a03b8:26","text":"在交互式渲染期间，Texture Manager 会把新纹理加入队列，并在转换完成前返回一个临时纹理。转换完成后，它会向渲染器发送更新，你的纹理就会显示出来。"}
{"id":"6df732bc763a5e473ddb38691d215777d17986291e1f83999d878f70703df745","item_id":"411c9a03b8:27","text":"当你启动"}
{"id":"320b5d80f8cfd184c57473d7081003135e0001480dac18583a0bdc748b361b88","item_id":"411c9a03b8:28","text":"Batch"}
{"id":"38596115fa6292b5ec3e278f4289002f38a7e8760fba7e7c9e5d6e35c0b38820","item_id":"411c9a03b8:29","text":"或"}
{"id":"324b134f57c70c729ae3dc4d298bb451656717d70523e942c1ce667b8024ea07","item_id":"411c9a03b8:30","text":"Preview"}
{"id":"7a9d520858a90aec05fb3e7f7bc4a90dd399e0bb6ce88991ed0d8ac1c16c1f94","item_id":"411c9a03b8:31","text":"渲染时，需要先完成所有纹理转换。"}
{"id":"74a883a037bc227f91891ab654a753d3a99f31ab06ae5b5d2b6e594a692b41f8","item_id":"411c9a03b8:32","text":"Settings（设置）"}
{"id":"2fb4019a35e427e8d595c79fe996407a01031a9e00ed0a7d174bfb1a0e455b90","item_id":"411c9a03b8:33","text":"Backend（后端）"}
{"id":"ae53da29c95119e66367d7f39363948dd1d1bd5c614eded711c9083f2ab01666","item_id":"411c9a03b8:35","text":"OpenImageIO"}
{"id":"e61b4bd509317f83023506d2e468f648ef6d852a6e027414c3c47811bc299754","item_id":"411c9a03b8:36","text":"会使用 OpenImageIO 库进行纹理转换，并启动 rmanoiiotool 进程。"}
{"id":"1432897a6136de54f3a8bfcc9f9fa87ead45c109731e5769a6e94887d555ce5b","item_id":"411c9a03b8:37","text":"Legacy"}
{"id":"fcd33491fd4b25706667e5ed1be24d7d7f0f05bb88b6d1353aec022d91379cf1","item_id":"411c9a03b8:38","text":"会使用 RenderMan 的 txmake 进程。此更改会在重新启动 Houdini 后生效。"}
{"id":"86308edc34eb996e8249789a2ca1ebe26be9d3e3d4cc095c40c6b2c180431235","item_id":"411c9a03b8:39","text":"Fallback Path（备用路径）"}
{"id":"aed7a626d6894e56c020b4dc8ba5cacf3752923c1980ed8cbb0ffbde63f72a13","item_id":"411c9a03b8:40","text":"：默认情况下，纹理管理器会将纹理保存在源图像旁边。如果由于任何原因无法保存到该目录，就会使用备用纹理路径。"}
{"id":"a5a14118d3787c600b40ee1b31996895aee3e945306aee7aa583320b79038768","item_id":"411c9a03b8:41","text":"Ignore Texture（忽略纹理）"}
{"id":"2c4d48ba6cb43e11655e9f3ce4b99bcf14515680ac7c1f9e6edb59b47b308e12","item_id":"411c9a03b8:42","text":"：列出不需要由 Texture Manager 转换的扩展名。"}
{"id":"7a1ec9fe6c3b483f5420a820892c4e29c5e76f6e1bbed4671e07de3371653e98","item_id":"411c9a03b8:43","text":"Workers（工作进程）"}
{"id":"5b5c7a1d139520c1623e7df97f4b2bbec5c61b0d10fc3ef0514a6e068437d024","item_id":"411c9a03b8:44","text":"：同时启动的工作进程数量。默认值为 2，但增加更多进程通常有助于加快队列速度。"}
{"id":"c1a9debf3289e60a4542202e5f0ac0f0e28216d22982a6015e5987bdd2c4aa11","item_id":"411c9a03b8:45","text":"Always Fallback（始终使用备用路径）"}
{"id":"2a06773fb3c1fb5e30d9e54d1cd49f38d08658912b66c92a933754cc748755d7","item_id":"411c9a03b8:46","text":"：始终将转换后的纹理保存到备用纹理目录。"}
{"id":"6d7da24cce60ca1e6bb665f8ae21b42acf39e7682e2e28e49198abf4832a1ad6","item_id":"411c9a03b8:47","text":"Keep Extensions（保留扩展名）："}
{"id":"df5f74fba6e23d4ec08e2be382fe17fd20a49d39856e23e7d70d4178f0548ee2","item_id":"411c9a03b8:48","text":"保留原始输入图像的扩展名。"}
{"id":"365075d1bf3ed18878ba0bb50360278b7eaa5973d32ed92fa1544238c09254cb","item_id":"411c9a03b8:49","text":"Show Advanced（显示高级选项）"}
{"id":"de00820c20d0798bcdfea66bc96c274730296eca30ee217ffd2f7c1313a5a16a","item_id":"411c9a03b8:50","text":"：在用户界面中显示更多高级选项。"}
{"id":"ac691ef402cedfb9e5d4fc9c69e96b4da61450ff3c963d2109a29b8017671344","item_id":"411c9a03b8:51","text":"Texture Manager Configuration（纹理管理器配置）"}
{"id":"28f9c5f29c315e447dab089cb8421ad9f5b4d41bb58739df7aae2ffc8b76d2f9","item_id":"411c9a03b8:52","text":"纹理管理器会根据以下内容，使用一组规则选择最佳的 OpenImageIO/txmake 参数："}
{"id":"817286398903927d82102f356c05028a744b0c060ed7e3cf3889d5036e0aa990","item_id":"411c9a03b8:53","text":"使用该纹理的节点类型："}
{"id":"9c565f69bdff2946a2c330087801747224a24450ff1ecc9d76073b794d6a768f","item_id":"411c9a03b8:56","text":"该节点类型的一组基础参数"}
{"id":"729b1b9ad609deadbd2fc582203e618a0ca6b28001b3784fd88beb9b9d5e4062","item_id":"411c9a03b8:57","text":"在考虑文件名、位深等因素时，用于修改基础参数的一条或多条规则。"}
{"id":"ffb293a69209f66f43c389807c6c8f15753ac9024411d2377f4ea91847550458","item_id":"411c9a03b8:58","text":"Custom（自定义）设置可以通过"}
{"id":"f8a4c31b96f0fe7c6ba6d9c811d9db4125819a3d96c5b8690cafc31e88512018","item_id":"411c9a03b8:59","text":"ocio configuration（OCIO 配置）定义"}
{"id":"31bd712e5452f84631219a283742ce7e99d305f9203083ec84f48184a1945099","item_id":"411c9a03b8:61","text":"默认规则是为效率而构建的；除非有特定的流水线需求，否则你不应需要修改它们。"}
{"id": "cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8", "item_id": "411c9a03b8:5", "text": "。"}
{"id": "6201111b83a0cb5b0922cb37cc442b9a40e24e3b1ce100a4bb204f4c63fd2ac0", "item_id": "411c9a03b8:14", "text": "和"}
{"id": "e7ac0786668e0ff0f02b62bd04f45ff636fd82db63b1104601c975dc005f3a67", "item_id": "411c9a03b8:34", "text": "："}
{"id": "7175517a370b5cd2e664e3fd29c4ea9db5ce17058eb9772fe090a5485e49dad6", "item_id": "411c9a03b8:54", "text": "或"}
